725689f-a.text: 85th Street, north from Astoria Boulevard, showing the thoroughfare shortly after it was constructed . All this land was formerly the Kouwenhoven farm. The cottage shown in View 2 is at 24th Avenue. Views 1 and 2: October 19, 1935. P. L. Sperr.
